premise_source_doc_sentence: A perpetrator can escape a crime scene by running , riding a horse , driving a getaway car , or riding with a getaway driver .
The Mahindra Scorpio Getaway is essentially the second vehicle launched by Mahindra on the Mahindra Scorpio platform .
In the Australian and New Zealand markets the Mahindra Scorpio Getaway has been launched as the Mahindra Pik-Up in 2014 .
The Getaway Plan found commercial success in Australia upon the release of their debut studio album , Other Voices , Other Rooms , in 2008 .
On 12 August 2013 , The Getaway Plan released their first ever self funded record ; A double a-sided single entitled `` Lovesick/Mirrors '' .
